headline: Intuitive Surgical (NasdaqGS:ISRG) Sees 10% Dip Despite Q4 Revenue Surge To US$2 Billion
summary: In recent developments, Intuitive Surgical (NasdaqGS:ISRG) experienced a 10% price decline last quarter, a period that included substantial corporate activities and broader market volatility. The company's fourth-quarter results showed impressive growth, with a revenue increase to $2.4 billion and net income rising to $685.7 million.
